Let’s Make Soup 🍲 Southern Style!
 
Fall is here and the chilly weather is amongst us so I love to make comfort meals that remind me of my Mom’s kitchen growing up. Enjoy 🫶🏾 

You Will Need The Following:
- Tomato Soup
- Beef Broth
- Frozen Vegetables 
- Onion Soup Mix
- Stewed Tomatoes 
- Potatoes 
- Ground Beef or Ground Turkey
- Beef Neck Bones for Added Flavor
#fallvibes #fall #soup #soupseason #cozymeal #comfortfood

Lasagna Soup 🍜  Delish 😋
I made the viral lasagna soup! 10 out of 10! 

You Will Need:
- Yellow Onion
- Garlic Cloves or Minced
- 1/2 lb hot or mild Italian sausage 
- 1/2 lb of lean ground beef
- 2 T tomato paste
* Salt & Pepper to taste
1-2 T Tony’s Seasoning 
1  teaspoon dried parsley 
1 teaspoon dried oregano 
1 teaspoon Italian seasoning 
1/2 red pepper 
24 oz marinara 
1/2 cup heavy cream
4 to 6 cups chicken stock
1/2 pound of lasagna 
-fresh basil 
CHEESE TOPPING < 1 cup of Parmesan, mozzarella, & ricotta. 1/4 cup of fresh parsley 

#lasagnasoup #easysoup #souprecipe #comfortfood #fallsoup #soup #fall #fallvibes

Holiday Lemon Drop 🎄🍸
You’re going to want to save this to make later!
Everyone knows I love a good lemon drop, and this holiday lemon drop has quickly become a festive favorite. So good!
Recipe: 
2 oz Vodka 
1.5 oz lemon juice 
1 oz of cranberry juice
.5 oz of simple syrup 
Rim glass with sugar and garnish with cranberries. 
Cheers to the holidays!

🥂 The Best Year of My Life Recap 

I can honestly say without hesitation, this year, 2023,  has been the BEST YEAR of My Adult life! 
God overfilled my cup. He overly fulfilled his promises to me. 
Any and everything I could dream, came true. 
Everything I’ve ever prayed for. 

Special thank you to My Man @thedopeeducator ! Saying Yes is the best decision I’ve ever made! God really sent me my very own Prince Charming that is a Man of God. Thankful that God saw fit to let us not only cross paths when I least expected, but allowed us to begin building our very own together. 

I’m so thankful for the last 365 days, and looking forward to all he has in store in the next 365 days for us and our family. 
Happy New Year ✨🥂
.
.
.
.
